    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你试过和熊玩过牌吗? 但熊不会打牌。.. 那么，在这个令人难以置信的游戏，你必须觉得自己像一个熊谁是试图打牌，但没有什么工作了他。 他所能做的就是粉碎周围的一切，尖叫 GOOOOOAL！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >就像一个平台游戏，但反过来！ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验令人难以置信的游戏在你的指尖在垂直平台游戏类型，在那里你必须爬得越来越高，击败敌人在你的方式，并找出什么是在最顶端？ 它就在那儿</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一个独特的游戏基于标志性的米姆关于熊! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让你内心深处的幻想成真，感觉就像一只熊，打破周围的一切，尖叫咕咕！!! 🐻</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024540/extras/fab48860330a6c918c5e60c1de54880e.poster.avif?t=1771358676\" width=560 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024540/extras/fab48860330a6c918c5e60c1de54880e.webm?t=1771358676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024540/extras/fab48860330a6c918c5e60c1de54880e.mp4?t=1771358676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解决独特的难题和玩令人兴奋的迷你游戏! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个具有挑战性和独特的游戏，提供高品质的沉浸和令人难以置信的乐趣一整天！ 只有5％的人能够解决这个谜语</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024540/extras/165b74f35a4fea519b669b6af253659c.poster.avif?t=1771358676\" width=560 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024540/extras/165b74f35a4fea519b669b6af253659c.webm?t=1771358676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024540/extras/165b74f35a4fea519b669b6af253659c.mp4?t=1771358676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏是中文的！ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本场比赛是完全翻译和配音成中文，以便在游戏过程中没有分心！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快推</strong>！GOOOOOOAL!!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024540/extras/e24c30769d4a7ce5c98680526c6cb2d3.poster.avif?t=1771358676\" width=560 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024540/extras/e24c30769d4a7ce5c98680526c6cb2d3.webm?t=1771358676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024540/extras/e24c30769d4a7ce5c98680526c6cb2d3.mp4?t=1771358676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
